page.content: Marsden Wilson Bergman Whalley Stark Heap Jones Koppada Thomson Whittaker Davis Rixon Colling Hornby Ellis Webb Gartell Dobson Platts Jankowski Copsey Parfitt Crombie Clegg Sharples Acuna Jones Salt Cubbins Hodson Ellis Blofeld Keen Dunn Burton Houghton Salmon Johnson Beech Kirkham Camm Cochrane Ruman Kennerley Powell Nuttall Bithell Lees Latham Hicklin Richmond Muir Singh Farrimond Eastwood Fletcher Hartley ONeill Strefford Robinson Redcliffe Loughlin Payne Rimmer The children live in the village or in an area about two Kilometres away called Normoss or along the road connecting these areas. The school although CE serves children of other denominations and faiths. Most of the parents work away from the village in the neighbouring larger towns such as Blackpool or Preston.
